        {
          "id": "AwsSolutions-IAM5",
          "reason": "The export role needs s3:PutObject on the dynamodb-exports/* object prefix; DynamoDB chooses the object keys (AWSDynamoDB/<ExportId>/...), so a prefix wildcard is the narrowest possible grant.",
